&lt;p&gt;I will actually open a separate Jira for this when i get home.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14644666" author="rmetzger" created="Tue, 28 Jul 2015 17:10:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I see that its tricky to implement a test for this, but its one of the main features of Flink, so its worth the effort (in my opinion)&lt;br/&gt;
